    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The five nominal validation points spanning 3–5 L/min and 3000–4500 RPM demonstrate CFD prediction of relative hemolysis index within 6% of experimental values, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Software QA, grid convergence, and test condition replication all confirmed. Edge-case operating conditions (maximum-speed high-shear-stress impeller tip region at ≥5500 RPM and near-stall minimum-flow at ≤1.5 L/min) are addressed in companion work. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for the COU as defined.",
